chart.name: Job Stages
chart.programText:
C = data('gauge.spark.job.num_completed_stages').publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = data('gauge.spark.job.num_skipped_stages').publish(label='D', enable=False)
E = data('gauge.spark.job.num_failed_stages').publish(label='E', enable=False)
F = data('gauge.spark.job.num_active_stages').publish(label='F', enable=False)
H = (C + D+E+F).publish(label='H')
